 "font": "Default",
 "html": "<style>\n    .print-format p {\n            font-family: Liberation Sans, Arial, Helvetica;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n            vertical-align: middle;\n        }\n    .print-format th {\n        text-align: center;\n        background-color: #808080 !important;\n        font-size: 9pt;\n        color: white;\n    }\n    .print-format tbody > tr {\n        page-break-after: always;\n        page-break-inside: avoid;\n    }\n    .print-format table {\n        border: black;\n        page-break-inside: auto;\n    }\n    \n    @media print {\n        .body_container {\n            /* 0.75 inch = 19,05 mm; 72 -> 96 dpi = Faktor 0,75 => 14,3 mm  */\n            /* left: -14.3mm; */\n            margin-left: 15mm;\n            margin-right: 10mm;\n            /*left: 7.5mm;*/\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .red_bar_right {\n            position:absolute;\n            display:block;\n            width: 7mm;\n            top: 0mm;\n            left: 203mm;\n            height: 282.3mm;\n            background-color: #b71c25;\n            border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 10px;\n        }\n        .red_bar_right_followup {\n            position:absolute;\n            display:block;\n            width: 7mm;\n            left: 203mm;\n            height: 282.3mm;\n            background-color: #b71c25;\n            border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 10px;\n        }\n        .red_label {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0mm;\n            width: 152mm;\n            height: 15.873mm;\n            background-color: #b71c25;\n        }\n        .contact_person {\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 146mm;\n            width: 50mm;\n            top: 75mm;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n            /* Text format */\n        }\n        .quotation_data {\n            margin-left: 15mm;\n            position:absolute;\n            top: 87mm;\n        }\n        .item_name {\n            word-break: break-all;\n            font-size: 9pt;\n        }\n        .contact_person p {\n            font-size: 9pt;\n        }\n        .salutation {\n            margin-left: 15mm;\n            position:absolute;\n            width: 100%;\n            top: 120mm;\n        }\n        .salutation p {\n            font-size: 9pt;\n        }\n        .items {\n        }\n        .price {\n            text-align: right;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n        }\n        td {\n            font-size: 9pt;\n        }\n    }\n    .new_page {\n        height: 40mm;\n    }\n    .logo {\n        position: absolute;\n        top: 0mm;\n        left: 158.1mm;\n        width: 36mm;\n        height: 17.1mm;\n    }\n    \n\n</style>\n\n<div>\n    {% if letter_head and not no_letterhead %}\n        {{ letter_head }}\n    {% endif %}\n</div>\n<div class=\"red_bar_right\"></div>\n<div class=\"contact_person\">\n    <p>\n        <b>Ihr Ansprechpartner:</b><br>\n        {{ doc.quotation_owner_name }}<br>\n        Tel. {{frappe.db.get_value(\"User\", {\"name\":doc.quotation_owner}, \"phone\") }}<br>\n        {{ doc.quotation_owner }}<br>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        M&uuml;nchen, den {{ doc.get_formatted(\"transaction_date\") }}\n    </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"quotation_data\">\n    <table border=1>\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th style=\"width:40mm\">Angebot</th>\n                <th style=\"width:75mm\">\n                    {% if doc.opportunity %}\n                        {{frappe.db.get_value(\"Opportunity\", {\"name\":doc.opportunity}, \"description\") }}\n                    {% else %}\n                        Kein Titel angegeben - Alternativen besprechen.\n                    {% endif %}\n                </th>\n            </tr>   \n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>\n                    Angebots-Nr.<br>\n                    G&uuml;ltig bis:<br>\n                    RH Accountnummer:<br>\n                    Ansprechpartner:\n                </td>\n                <td>\n                    {{ doc.name }}<br>\n                    {{ doc.get_formatted(\"valid_till\") }}<br>\n                    RH-No. einf&uuml;gen<br>\n                    {{ doc.customer_name}}\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"body_container\">\n    <p>\n        Sehr \n        {% if \"Hr\" in frappe.db.get_value(\"Lead\", {\"name\":doc.party_name}, \"salutation_2\") %}\n            geehrter Herr\n        {% else %}\n            geehrte Frau\n        {% endif %}\n        {{ doc.customer_name }},<br>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        vielen Dank f\u00fcr Ihre Anfrage. Gerne unterbreiten wir Ihnen folgendes Angebot:\n    </p>\n\n    <table class=\"items table table-bordered\">\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th style=\"width: 2%\">Pos</th>\n                <th>Artikelnr.</th>\n                <th class=\"item_name\">Produkt</th>\n                <th>St&uuml;ck</th>\n                <th style=\"width: 10%\">Einzel-</th>\n                <th style=\"width: 10%\">Gesamtpreis</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n        {% for item in doc.items %}\n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"text-align: center;\">{{ loop.index }}</td>\n                <td style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">{{ item.item_code }}</td>\n                <td>\n                    {{ item.item_name}}<br>\n                    <br>\n                    {% if item.additional_notes %}\n                        <b>{{ item.additional_notes }}</b>\n                    {% endif %}\n                </td>\n                <td style=\"text-align: center;\">{{ item.get_formatted(\"qty\") }}</td>\n                <td class=\"price\">{{ item.get_formatted(\"rate\").replace(doc.currency,'') }} {{ doc.currency }}</td>\n                <td class=\"price\">{{ item.get_formatted(\"amount\").replace(doc.currency,'') }} {{ doc.currency }}</td>\n            </tr>\n            {% if item.page_break %}\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"page-break\"></div>\n{% endif %}\n{% endfor %}\n<div class=\"red_bar_right_followup\"></div>\n<div class=\"body_container clearfix\">\n    <table class=\"items table table-bordered\">\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th style=\"width: 2%\">Pos</th>\n                <th>Artikelnr.</th>\n                <th class=\"item_name\">Produkt</th>\n                <th>St&uuml;ck</th>\n                <th style=\"width: 10%\">Einzel-</th>\n                <th style=\"width: 10%\">Gesamtpreis</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n            \n            <tr>\n                <td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align: right; border: 0;\">Summe:</td>\n                <td style=\"text-align: right; border-right: 0; border-bottom: 0; white-space: nowrap;\">{{ doc.get_formatted(\"total\").replace(doc.currency,'') }} {{ doc.currency }}</td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <div class=\"closing\" style=\"background-color: green;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">\n            Das Angebot ist freibleibend. Alle Preise verstehen sich rein netto zzgl. der gesetzlichen Umsatzsteuer. Es gelten unsere Allgemeinen Gesch&auml;ftsbedingungen (www.linux-ag.com/allgemeine-geschaeftsbedingungen).\n        </p>\n        <p>\n            Versandkosten sind nicht Bestandteil des Angebots und werden dem Kunden ggf. in Rechnung gestellt. Reisekosten sind im Angebot nicht enthalten und werden extra berechnet. Diese werden nach angefallenem Aufwand zu den jeweils geltenden Abrechnungss\u00e4tzen in Rechnung gestellt.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n            F\u00fcr Fragen stehe ich Ihnen jederzeit zur Verf&uuml;gung\n        </p>\n        <p>\n            Mit freundlichen Gr&uuml;&szlig;en<br>\n            {{ doc.quotation_owner_name }}\n        </p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div>\n    <div id=\"footer-html\" class=\"visible-pdf\">\n        {% if not no_letterhead and footer %}\n        <div class=\"letter-head-footer\" style=\"margin-top: 30mm; height: 10mm;\">\n            {{ footer }}\n        </div>\n        {% endif %}\n    </div>\n</div>",
